metadata.name: Serenity
metadata.description: A street lamp stands alone in the foreground, basking in the warm glow of the setting sun. As the dark clouds in the background begin to clear, they are creating a stunning contrast. In the distance, the trail of an airplane adds a sense of movement and perspective to the scene. This moment of transition from darkness to light is both beautiful and serene, with the street lamp serving as a symbol of stability amidst the changing sky.
